WF-003 | Open delinquency bucket detail from Buckets table | actor: <role> | branch: none | terminal: Bucket Name (link) | on_success: navigates to Delinquency_Bucket_Detail
WF-004 | Create a delinquency bucket (with one or more ranges) | actor: <role> | branch: none | terminal: Create | on_success: creates delinquency bucket; when a linked loan becomes overdue the system automatically classifies it into the appropriate range based on days past due for portfolio-at-risk reporting, provisioning calculations, and collection workflow triggers
